      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster, free of any swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, and has been professionally treated with a high-end ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is an immaculate time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with absolutely no bolster wear, and every switch and dial operates with tactile precision. This car has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never been driven in rain or inclement weather. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, benefiting from a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule documented in a comprehensive service binder. The engine bay is detailed to a mirror finish, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. For the buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity to own a flawless example of automotive excellence.",
